{"word":"G172 - ἄκακος - ákakos - ak'-ak-os - Harmless","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἄκακος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">ákakos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ak'-ak-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Harmless</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"கபடில்லாத, குற்றமற்ற - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"without guile or fraud, harmless; free from guilt, fearing no evil from others, distrusting no one"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and <a href=\"#/G2556 - κακός - kakós - kak-os'/2556\">G2556</a>; <i>not bad</i>, that is, (objectively) <i>innocent</i> or (subjectively) <i>unsuspecting:</i> - harmless, simple.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1573/1573\">G1573</a>, <a href=\"#/G172/172\">G172</a>, <a href=\"#/G2549/2549\">G2549</a>, <a href=\"#/G2550/2550\">G2550</a>, <a href=\"#/G2554/2554\">G2554</a>, <a href=\"#/G2555/2555\">G2555</a>, <a href=\"#/G2556/2556\">G2556</a>, <a href=\"#/G2557/2557\">G2557</a>, <a href=\"#/G420/420\">G420</a>"}]}